Program: Discovery
Title: Sutra Medieval Hospital
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwyj
Last Broadcast Date: 01 September 1997
Why waste could hold clues as to the day to day practice of a hospital 800 years ago. Findings at the Sutra hospital in Scotland has challenged medical thinking. Also in the programme, how advances in scanning have brought about a boom in research into the brain and the comet Chiron. Presenter: Graham Easton. Show less